2405			// Also, enable and disable as one command, as if any operation fails
2406			// we'd bubble up the error anyways, and we save a lot of time doing this.
2407			// Presets must be done individually as we don't consider a failed preset
2408			// as an error, but it would cause other presets that would have succeeded
2409			// to not go through.
